casebody.data:
No. 121,

Mise.

Taylor v. Dennis, Warden. Nesbitt Elmore, Thurgood Marshall, Marian Wynn Perry and Frank D. Reeves for petitioner.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of certiorari granted. Petition for writ of certiorari granted.

Mr. Justice Black took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications. *891A. A. Carmichael, Attorney General of Alabama, Bernard F. Sykes and James L. Screws, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.
